Package solver.variables

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BoolVar

    CPRU r544: remove default implementation
    IntVar
    Interface for integer variables.
    IVariableMonitor<V extends Variable>
    A monitor for Variable, to observe variable modification (for integer variable : value removals, bounds modification or instantiation) and do something right after the modification.
    RealVar
    An interface to declare variable for continuous constraints (solved using IBEX).
    SetVar
    A Set Variable is defined by a domain which is a set interval [kernel,envelope] The kernel is the set of elements that must belong to every single solution.
    Variable
    Created by IntelliJ IDEA.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Task
    Container representing a task: It ensures that: start + duration = end
    VariableFactory
    A factory to create variables (boolean, integer, set, graph, task and real) and views (most of them rely on integer variable).
    VF
    A short-named version of VariableFactory
